<plot>George Morales is an accomplished neurosurgeon living the "American Dream." But, when he injures himself, he is forced to convalesce at the home of his estranged son, Nate, a pro bono attorney living in the middle of the barrio. George must now come face to face with his Mexican roots, the path that he has chosen, and the son that he has left behind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?541784</url></doc>
